---
const principles = [
	{
		title: "Honesty over sales.",
		description:
			"If AI isn't the right solution for your problem, we'll tell you. We'd rather lose a deal than sell you something that doesn't work. Counterintuitively, this is also why clients trust us enough to come back for more.",
	},
	{
		title: "Results over impressions.",
		description:
			"We measure success by hours saved and teams that actually use what we built. Sophisticated technology that nobody opens is a failure. We'd rather ship something boring that people use every day.",
	},
	{
		title: "We want you to outgrow us.",
		description:
			"Every engagement includes training. Every project leaves your team more capable than before. Our goal is for you to need us less over time. We consider it a success when you do.",
	},
	{
		title: "You can see our prices right now.",
		description:
			"Our prices are published. Our process is documented. Our recommendations are explained in plain language. You deserve to understand what you're buying and why before the first call.",
	},
	{
		title: "People over technology.",
		description:
			"AI is a tool. Your people are the strategy. We design every solution around the humans who'll use it, their workflows and their daily reality. The best AI in the world is worthless if the team doesn't trust it.",
	},
];
---

<section class="flex flex-col gap-12 bg-foreground px-4 md:px-8 lg:px-16 py-20 w-full">
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 w-full">
    <span class="font-heading text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[2px] text-accent">WHAT WE BELIEVE</span>
    <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl lg:text-[40px] font-bold text-background text-center tracking-[-1.5px]">
      Our principles. Non-negotiable.
    </h2>
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-col w-full">
    {principles.map((p) => (
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 py-8 border-t border-border w-full">
        <span class="font-heading text-[22px] font-bold text-accent w-full md:w-[320px] shrink-0">{p.title}</span>
        <p class="font-body text-base text-secondary-foreground leading-[1.7] flex-1">{p.description}</p>
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>
</section>
